---
// Bloom & Co Florist — SOFT PASTEL BOTANICAL
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bloom & Co Florist — Demo | SiteGenius</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600&family=Mulish:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:'Mulish',sans-serif;color:#2d3a2d;background:#f7f5f0}h1,h2,h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif}
    .demo-bar{background:#6b7c5e;color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:10px;font-size:13px;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:999}.demo-bar a{color:#d4e0c8;font-weight:700}
    .hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding-top:50px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f7f5f0,#ede8df)}
    .hero-inner{max-width:700px;padding:0 24px}
    .hero .tag{display:inline-block;border:1px solid #b8c5a8;color:#6b7c5e;padding:6px 20px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.8rem;margin-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
    .hero h1{font-size:4rem;line-height:1.15;color:#2d3a2d;font-weight:400}.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:#8a6d8a}
    .hero p{margin-top:20px;font-size:1.05rem;color:#5a6d56;line-height:1.8}
    .hero-btn{display:inline-block;margin-top:32px;padding:16px 40px;background:#6b7c5e;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;transition:.3s}.hero-btn:hover{background:#5a6a4e}
    .grid{padding:100px 24px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
    .grid h2{text-align:center;font-size:2.6rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:48px}
    .cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px}
    .card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e8e3da;overflow:hidden;transition:.3s}.card:hover{box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.06);transform:translateY(-4px)}
    .card-img{height:160px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:4rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0ece4,#e8ddd0)}
    .card-body{padding:24px;text-align:center}.card-body h3{font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:4px;font-weight:500}.card-body .price{color:#8a6d8a;font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:8px}.card-body p{font-size:.82rem;color:#7a8a72;line-height:1.6}
    .cta{background:#6b7c5e;padding:80px 24px;text-align:center;color:#fff}.cta h2{font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:12px}.cta p{opacity:.8;margin-bottom:28px}.cta a{display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;background:#fff;color:#6b7c5e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.85rem}
    @media(max-width:768px){.hero h1{font-size:2.6rem}.cards{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:400px;margin:0 auto}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="demo-bar">🌸 Demo by <a href="/">SiteGenius</a> — <a href="/get-a-quote">Get yours today</a></div>
  <section class="hero"><div class="hero-inner"><div class="tag">🌸 Same-Day Delivery</div><h1>Flowers That<br><em>Speak Volumes</em></h1><p>Handcrafted bouquets for every occasion. Delivered fresh to your door in Auckland.</p><a href="/get-a-quote" class="hero-btn">Shop Bouquets</a></div></section>
  <section class="grid"><h2>Our Collections</h2><div class="cards">
    <div class="card"><div class="card-img">🌹</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Romantic Roses</h3><div class="price">From $65</div><p>Classic long-stem red roses in stunning arrangements.</p></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-img">🌻</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Seasonal Wildflowers</h3><div class="price">From $55</div><p>Fresh, locally grown seasonal blooms.</p></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-img">💐</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Wedding Florals</h3><div class="price">From $250</div><p>Bespoke bridal bouquets and venue styling.</p></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-img">🕊️</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Sympathy & Tribute</h3><div class="price">From $80</div><p>Elegant wreaths to honour loved ones.</p></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-img">🏢</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Corporate</h3><div class="price">From $45/wk</div><p>Weekly fresh flowers for your office.</p></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-img">🎁</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Gift Hampers</h3><div class="price">From $90</div><p>Flowers paired with chocolates or wine.</p></div></div>
  </div></section>
  <section class="cta"><h2>Send Something Beautiful</h2><p>📍 Parnell Village, Auckland · Free delivery over $80</p><a href="/get-a-quote">Order Now →</a></section>
</body>
</html>
